channel.title: Friend can not connect to my 508 server
channel.description: I'm not sure if it is a problem with his client, as he had to go right after he installed everything and tested, but I was wondering what possible problems there was to be had. Before you ask, I have a No-IP redirect, and have port 43594 forwarded. It would also be great if someone was willing to PM me to try and connect to see if it's just him that I need to fix. Thanks much in advance. Rep will be given.
